The paper deals with hand gesture recognition and text input method for AR/VR wearable devices, which involves computer vision, human-computer interaction, multimedia, information retrieval, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), followed by cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
